13:52.900 --> 13:55.835
There were just
so many questions
coming at me...

13:55.903 --> 13:57.604
And I, I got nervous
and panicked,

13:57.670 --> 13:59.940
and I started
mixing things up
and forgetting things.

14:00.007 --> 14:01.508
It's okay.

14:01.574 --> 14:05.178
You're not the only person
that's forgotten
about foreplay.

14:05.245 --> 14:08.581
Oh, I'm sorry.
I thought you liked
having more time to read.

14:08.648 --> 14:11.618
Okay, thank you
for coming over.
We appreciate it.

14:17.624 --> 14:19.927
