about sex from now on.

14:22.996 --> 14:24.364
Good rule.

14:25.432 --> 14:27.167
(CHUCKLES)

14:27.234 --> 14:29.236
(DOOR CLOSES)
Man, can you believe her?

14:29.302 --> 14:30.570
What a mess
she made!

14:30.637 --> 14:32.305
Oh, really?
So this is Julie's fault?

14:32.372 --> 14:34.007
Well, it's not mine.

14:34.074 --> 14:36.676
If you recall,
I'm the one who said Molly
should give him the talk.

14:37.844 --> 14:39.812
If you had done
your job as a parent,

14:39.879 --> 14:42.382
