needed to ask Julie.

14:42.449 --> 14:46.019
Wow, I didn't think
about it...
(LAUGHING)

14:46.086 --> 14:48.688
Why are you dressed
like the Hamburglar's
naughty daughter?

14:48.755 --> 14:50.857
(LAUGHS)

14:50.924 --> 14:52.459
Oh, come on!
I'm sorry!

14:52.525 --> 14:54.394
Oh, come on!
No, no,
I didn't mean that!

14:54.461 --> 14:56.829
I shouldn't have shirked
my responsibility!
(LAUGHS)

15:01.568 --> 15:02.702
Hey.

15:03.703 --> 15:04.737
Hey.

15:07.474 --> 15:10.110
Did you, uh,
get my text?
(PEN TAPS)

15:10.177 --> 15:12.379
I did.

15:12.445 --> 15:14.214
Uh, so, should we
go somewhere and, uh...

15:14.281 --> 15:15.715
I'm breaking up
with you!

15:16.249 --> 15:17.684
Attaboy!

15:19.152 --> 15:22.189
I'm sorry. What?
And you know what?
It is your loss!

15:22.255 --> 15:23.656
I don't even like
Thai food,

15:23.723 --> 15:26.526
but I eat it with you
all the time!

15:26.593 --> 15:29.729
I even go so far
as to make
adorable puns about it!

15:29.796 --> 15:31.364
But you know what,
if that is not
enough for you,

15:31.431 --> 15:34.301
well, then you can
Thai me a river!

15:38.205 --> 15:40.240
Oh, God, were you
not coming here
to break up with me?

15:40.307 --> 15:41.774
(SIGHS)
You know what?
Forget what I said.

15:41.841 --> 15:43.543
Want to grab dinner?
Hey, how about Thai? Mmm!

15:43.610 --> 15:45.312
Clark, Clark,
Clark, Clark!

15:45.712 --> 15:47.214
(SIGHS)

15:47.280 --> 15:48.982
I actually did
come here to break up
with you.

15:49.049 --> 15:52.119
Aha!
The plot maintains
its exact thickness!

15:52.185 --> 15:54.121
(MOUTHING)

15:54.187 --> 15:55.788
See, I knew
you were going to,

15:55.855 --> 15:58.091
so that's why I broke up
with you, but...

15:58.158 --> 15:59.792
God, I don't want to.
I don't want to either.

15:59.859 --> 16:02.129
Then why?
I don't know!

16:02.195 --> 16:03.496
When we first
started dating,

16:03.563 --> 16:05.165
you were this
hot-blooded nurse

16:05.232 --> 16:07.334
who knew exactly
what he wanted.

16:07.400 --> 16:09.436
And now you've become
a kind of pushover

16:09.502 --> 16:11.271
who just wants to do
whatever I want to do.

16:11.338 --> 16:12.772
Yeah, but that's just...

16:12.839 --> 16:14.574
It's because
I like you so much

16:14.641 --> 16:16.976
that I'm scared
I'm gonna screw this up.

16:17.044 --> 16:18.545
You won't
if you're yourself.

16:18.611 --> 16:20.513
I'm not gonna dump you
because you hate
Thai food.

16:20.580 --> 16:21.848
I'm not a monster.

16:21.914 --> 16:23.950
In my defense,
a guy did once
break up with me

16:24.017 --> 16:26.553
because instead
of saying "cashew,"
I say, "ca-shew!"

16:28.521 --> 16:31.858
I'm just as scared
of screwing this up
as you are.

16:31.924 --> 16:34.294
We have to just
be ourselves and hope
that that's enough.

16:34.361 --> 16:36.129
God, you're more
than enough.

16:36.196 --> 16:37.230
So are you.

16:40.567 --> 16:41.768
Aww!

16:42.869 --> 16:44.571
Come on,
let's get out of here.

16:44.637 --> 16:47.607
I have a few more opinions
to fill you in on,
starting with this jacket.

16:47.674 --> 16:48.875
(CHUCKLES) Yikes.

16:48.941 --> 16:50.043
Have a good night.

16:50.110 --> 16:51.911
Don't pander to them.
Okay.

16:52.845 --> 16:55.815
Ah. Good old PEB.

16:55.882 --> 16:57.950
Works every time.
No, it doesn't.

16:58.017 --> 17:00.019
Yeah? Well,
it worked on you.

17:00.887 --> 17:02.089
Yeah.

17:02.155 --> 17:03.856
I got wind of the fact
you were gonna dump me,

17:03.923 --> 17:05.125
and I beat you
to the punch.

17:05.658 --> 17:07.294
Oh.

17:07.360 --> 17:08.828
You thought
I was gonna break up
with you?

17:08.895 --> 17:11.064
Mmm-hmm.
Interesting.

17:11.131 --> 17:13.533
Well...
You were, weren't you?

17:14.167 --> 17:15.602
Maybe.

17:15.668 --> 17:17.204
Well, you know,
it doesn't matter.

17:17.270 --> 17:19.872
Point is,
you never got closure,
so you're still intrigued.

17:19.939 --> 17:21.441
(SCOFFS)

17:21.508 --> 17:23.210
Ha! I am not!

17:23.276 --> 17:24.444
No? (CHUCKLES)

17:24.511 --> 17:25.778
Well, you want
to go get dinner,

17:25.845 --> 17:27.847
followed by
an erotic re-awakening?

17:29.416 --> 17:31.151
Damn it, I do.
(CHUCKLES)

17:33.353 --> 17:34.421
(CHUCKLES)

17:37.824 --> 17:40.160
I can't resist
your sneaky ass.

17:46.899 --> 17:49.035
(DOOR OPENS)

17:49.102 --> 17:51.938
Hey, Al, I took
the Christmas lights down.

17:52.004 --> 17:53.906
I also got
your brakes fixed.

17:53.973 --> 17:56.609
Admittedly, I may have
waited a little long
on that one.

17:56.676 --> 18:00.280
I couldn't stop
when I pulled into Arturo's,
came in kind of hot.

18:00.347 --> 18:02.882
Unrelated,
you also got a new bumper.

18:02.949 --> 18:04.617
Well, that almost
makes up

18:04.684 --> 18:06.553
for delegating our
son's sexual education

18:06.619 --> 18:08.155
to someone who thought
heavy petting

18:08.221 --> 18:12.058
was what you do
to an overweight
house cat.

18:12.125 --> 18:15.162
Well, just so you know,
there's a reason
I never gave Dave the talk.

18:15.228 --> 18:17.864
Yeah. You're terrified
of awkward conversations,

18:17.930 --> 18:22.034
which is strange
because you create them
on a daily basis.

18:22.101 --> 18:24.737
Look, the thing is,
Dave's still
my little buddy.

18:24.804 --> 18:26.306
He's just
an innocent kid,

18:26.373 --> 18:28.775
getting his butt kicked
by his dad in Operation.

18:28.841 --> 18:30.510
I know you lost.

18:30.577 --> 18:32.979
Technically, we never
finished, but that's not
what's important here.

18:33.045 --> 18:35.382
Look, once he knows
all about adult stuff,

18:35.448 --> 18:38.451
he'll eventually stop
being my little boy,

18:38.518 --> 18:40.820
and I'm just not ready
for him to grow up yet.

18:40.887 --> 18:43.356
Okay. I get that.

18:43.423 --> 18:47.126
But part of being
a parent is putting
aside your own issues

18:47.194 --> 18:49.696
and being there
for your kids
when they need you.

18:49.762 --> 18:51.264
You're right, Al.

18:51.331 --> 18:53.566
All right,
I'll give him the talk.

18:53.633 --> 18:55.368
You know,
being a parent sucks.

18:55.435 --> 18:57.670
(BOTH CHUCKLE)
It sucks so bad.

18:57.737 --> 18:58.938
(LAUGHS)

18:59.005 --> 19:00.373
(KNOCK ON DOOR)

19:02.309 --> 19:04.143
Mom?
What happened?

19:04.211 --> 19:07.146
You're back in beige!

19:07.214 --> 19:10.650
Well, in the
20 minutes it took me
to get into that skirt,

19:10.717 --> 19:12.385
I had some time
to think.

19:12.452 --> 19:15.955
And I realized,
while I needed a change,

19:16.022 --> 19:18.791
this stuff just isn't me.

19:18.858 --> 19:21.093
I don't want my feet
to bleed on a Monday.

19:23.196 --> 19:26.399
I guess that's where
we're different.

19:26.466 --> 19:29.302
So, what are you
gonna do with all
the things we bought?

19:29.369 --> 19:31.538
I'll just return them.
Good call.

19:31.604 --> 19:33.172
(GASPS)

19:33.240 --> 19:35.342
Wait a minute!
You know what, Mom?
Hmm?

19:35.408 --> 19:37.109
What if you just gave
all that stuff to me?

19:37.176 --> 19:39.312
You'd do that for me?

19:39.379 --> 19:41.248
We're family.

19:41.314 --> 19:43.350
Well, here you go.

19:43.416 --> 19:46.253
I'm just so glad
that all worked out!

19:46.319 --> 19:48.355
Mmm, you're welcome.

19:52.659 --> 19:54.827
Dude, I think you just
got played.

19:54.894 --> 19:56.229
Uh, really?

19:56.296 --> 19:57.364
You knew?

19:57.430 --> 19:58.731
Then why did you
even give...

19:58.798 --> 20:01.133
Because she won't
always be interested

20:01.200 --> 20:03.670
in manipulating
her mother
for free clothes.

20:04.871 --> 20:06.239
Huh.

20:06.306 --> 20:09.008
I guess Dave's not
the only one
growing up too fast.

20:09.075 --> 20:11.778
We need to enjoy
these moments
while we can.

20:13.145 --> 20:15.315
You're right.

20:15.382 --> 20:17.584
Speaking of
enjoying moments...

20:17.650 --> 20:19.686
Maybe you and I
should have
the sex talk first,

20:19.752 --> 20:22.121
you know,
just to work out
any kinks.

20:23.256 --> 20:25.425
Or to work...

20:25.492 --> 20:27.226
In some kinks...
(LAUGHS)

20:27.294 --> 20:28.961
If you know
what I sayin'.

20:29.028 --> 20:30.530
I know what you sayin'.

20:30.597 --> 20:32.765
(BOTH LAUGH)

20:32.832 --> 20:34.367
Actually, can we skip
the foreplay?

20:34.434 --> 20:36.936
I just hurt my back
just doing this whole thing.
Yep.

20:42.875 --> 20:46.413
And because
these activities
take place beforehand,

20:46.479 --> 20:48.515
it's called "foreplay."

20:48.581 --> 20:49.849
Get it?
Got it.

20:49.916 --> 20:51.884
Thanks for telling me
all this stuff, Dad.

20:51.951 --> 20:53.252
You're welcome, buddy.

20:53.320 --> 20:55.322
Yeah, thank you,
Dr. Park.

20:55.388 --> 20:58.591
This has been
super informative.

20:58.658 --> 21:01.594
Like, a real eye-opener.

21:01.661 --> 21:04.697
Hey, is it okay if I call you
if I have any more questions?

21:04.764 --> 21:07.667
Any time.
I think I have
a good handle on it.

21:09.769 --> 21:12.439
Well, I've got to get
home to the cats.

21:12.505 --> 21:14.707
